                    },
                    "body": "Well, reading the reference guide, seems like is not a bug: http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/manual\/en\/zend.registry.html#zend.registry.using.array-object so the QuickStart needs to be fixed, http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/docs\/quickstart\/create-a-configuration-and-registry adding Zend_Registry::setInstance() code portion to the \"REGISTRY\" code sample.\n\n$registry = new Zend_Registry(array(), ArrayObject::ARRAY_AS_PROPS)\nZend_Registry::setInstance($registry);\n\n\n\n",
